<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0"><channel><title>Yo玩出个名堂</title><link>https://wxrss.reinject.top/9fd2f1699bcdfec0624fd7c7cc18a9d5/</link><description>An RSS feed.</description><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 12:32:42 +0800</lastBuildDate><generator>wxrss -- https://github.com/0xlane/wxrss</generator><item><title>主板性能天梯榜 英雄招募帖</title><link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4MjkwMjE5Ng==&amp;mid=2247489675&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7ab5491acde944172bb265ce31d872bf&amp;chksm=ea014328082b46f6a8d01e935a73957356ffa86f4d1d671da381cc24ac38b65d467dc5ab4834&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd</link><description><![CDATA[各位英雄，早~编撰《AM5主板天梯榜》，最难的部分在于主板供电规格的收集。媒体的拆解测试，是目前唯一的信息来源，但以高端为主，中低端信息严重缺失。AM4时代，很多板厂的低端不舍得给散热片，博主还能凭借]]></description><author>Yo玩出个名堂</author><pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 11:17:47 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>AM5主板性能天梯榜 二 B650 华硕篇</title><link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4MjkwMjE5Ng==&amp;mid=2247489657&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=cb1bec1804a105c892a0e59d7430b1c8&amp;chksm=ea3ff93793e502b006e55e24e17f66d3e806d65c48371e54fe2e5528fc3527856b1564b5ae8f&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd</link><description><![CDATA[要评华硕，先得理清供电PWM多相数字主控判断主板供电，一般人只会“数电感”。一颗电感对应一路供电，但绝不等同于一相供电多路供电，确实能分摊电流，降低Mos、电感温度，但是过流的总带宽仍由相数决定。供电]]></description><author>Yo玩出个名堂</author><pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 23:18:36 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>AM5主板天梯榜 番外 芯片组平台篇</title><link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4MjkwMjE5Ng==&amp;mid=2247489601&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=4664c3262c3d02928145851943f7f428&amp;chksm=ea912e9c2c0c1092fee6cb9d2864a2768195ddd9b145d62b501047b5da792d8bec060c97e429&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd</link><description><![CDATA[1995年，Socket 7平台问世。作为PC史上唯一的多厂商插座，6个品牌的CPU逐鹿春秋。凭借 3DNow! 浮点指令集，AMD K6-2 CPU表现惊艳，在3D游戏上力压Intel Pentiu]]></description><author>Yo玩出个名堂</author><pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 21:35:50 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>AM5主板天梯榜 二 B650 华硕篇 图片版</title><link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4MjkwMjE5Ng==&amp;mid=2247489569&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ce63f3359a9ca250690080350e574a90&amp;chksm=ea0a8d458f52a7ff81c1084835c9591fb13b75fcd978616765910ba0db83b1aa85029e7bdb8a&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd</link><description><![CDATA[]]></description><author>Yo玩出个名堂</author><pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 20:59:00 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>AM5主板性能天梯榜 一 B650 华擎篇</title><link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4MjkwMjE5Ng==&amp;mid=2247489548&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=17b5deceb7b76ae4f771fbaec7af2552&amp;chksm=ea0df14270f80f9921a44fb322b70f7349c23ece7365a957ee7ca6ca4422154467447f8b2d54&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd</link><description><![CDATA[2022年，个人电脑端，AMD使用Socket AM5接口，接替了史上最长青的Socket AM4插座，超威处理器进入DDR5时代。1331针脚的AM4插座，142w的PPT默认功耗墙，显然已经容不下]]></description><author>Yo玩出个名堂</author><pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 08:18:00 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>AM5主板天梯榜 一 B650 华擎篇 图片版</title><link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4MjkwMjE5Ng==&amp;mid=2247489539&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=dd07cbebead7634a564c229252fefdc2&amp;chksm=ea49e4d95e000dd14661cfce1d8919c20ae80c0a261f4c949c85fa08ee87b3b4a40e10c90df9&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd</link><description><![CDATA[]]></description><author>Yo玩出个名堂</author><pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 21:34:37 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>一周双响 硬核我在行</title><link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4MjkwMjE5Ng==&amp;mid=2247489452&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=5e22d466642f6b1efa2982fef5c0825d&amp;chksm=ea81058f869e550caf32c7491b0b9d9d68cb6544500a9e256dd63f147cdffcbb78acf9973657&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd</link><description><![CDATA[]]></description><author>Yo玩出个名堂</author><pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 08:58:54 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>二刷知乎</title><link>http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4MjkwMjE5Ng==&amp;mid=2247489425&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=13fee4f41673edb64acc13ae7b4cbae3&amp;chksm=eaa191ce014af8e450c259b2613200cfa61acd54d2faf987a78f544870a3429df9e0127d9a8a&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd</link><description><![CDATA[]]></description><author>Yo玩出个名堂</author><pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 11:42:42 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>用过就再也回不去了的工具软件 